{"tid":982224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大修訂旅遊警告 指中國有「任意強制執法」風險","createTime":"2019-01-15T02:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T05:13:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"30f852517ba08e0541a4b9610c627d6405313828","tid":982224,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T02:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190115/large/1547518070_4e25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190115%2Flarge%2F1547518070_4e25.jpg&h=8acdf195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國及加拿大的關係日趨緊張，就在中方昨重審加拿大男子謝倫伯格（Robert Lloyd Schellenberg）走私毒品案並改判死刑後，加拿大修訂對中國的旅遊警示，警告赴中國的公民注意當局「任意強制執法」風險。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大是維持對中國的旅遊警示級別，不過就更新有關警示內容。加拿大總理杜魯多（Justin Trudeau）昨曾在謝倫伯格判刑後，批評中國隨意判處死刑，他高度關注事件。<br />\n<br />\n中加關係自華為副董事長孟晚舟案後急轉直下，中方後來以「涉嫌從事危害國家安全活動」為由拘捕加拿大前外交官康明凱（Michael Kovrig）和加籍商人斯帕沃（Michael Spavor）等人，被視為是報復。加方已多次批評中方任意執法，要求立即放人。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院本月初亦曾向中國發出新旅遊警示，提醒公民前往中國旅行時要謹言慎行，慎防中國任意執法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190115/59143780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190115%2F59143780&d=7Q0TnbiuGBwu1kYG%2F7S3upZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=bad6d2e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190115%2F59143780&h=daa939ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190115/59143780</a>"},{"pid":"30df94079c8b4f48c5f55ca9370a628d583e9bbc","tid":982224,"uid":143260,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:00:23.000Z","msg":"中國或許成為最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}